'The Murmur Years' is a comprehensive collection of the bands most loved tracks hand-picked from over ten years. Featuring 'The Futurist', written exclusively for this release as well as a collection of live favorites and covers such as, 'Rock the Casbah' and 'Born to Run', 'The Murmur Years' also draws on material from SFK's early EPs, as well as the five studio albums in 33 tracks. With numerous accolades including 13 ARIA nominations, nods from Rolling Stone for Album Of The Year, Single Of The Year, [[&]] Best Band, and repeatedly making Triple J's Hottest 100, this is the ultimate SFK collection.
